# VCS / editor / OS
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.dockerignore
**/.editorconfig
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/.DS_Store
*~

# Docs (not needed to build the image)
**/*.md
LICENSE

# Deployment / tooling (Helm chart, pipelines, scripts) — not part of the binary
**/infrastructure
**/start
Dockerfile*

# Local secrets / examples — never bake into the image (secrets come from the CSI mount)
**/secrets.example
**/.env

# Go build output & test artifacts
main
RepoUniqueIdentifier
RepoUniqueNormalisedIdentifier
*.exe
*.test
*.out
